1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,740
[Episode 60]
[2027 Student Drama Project]

2
00:00:05,290 --> 00:00:09,130
Hey, you've been helping me so much.
Have you finished your thesis?

3
00:00:09,330 --> 00:00:12,850
-The deadline is coming up-
-Oh, don't worry-

4
00:00:13,570 --> 00:00:16,930
I'll just have Taji
handle it for me

5
00:00:17,530 --> 00:00:23,850
He has plenty of people working for him,
and they're all incredibly skilled

6
00:00:24,410 --> 00:00:26,930
It'll definitely be done in time

7
00:00:26,930 --> 00:00:30,010
-Ouch-
-Hey, are you okay?-

8
00:00:43,010 --> 00:00:43,890
Hold on

9
00:00:53,890 --> 00:00:55,650
There we go

10
00:01:02,290 --> 00:01:05,370
Come on, give me your other finger too

11
00:01:09,530 --> 00:01:10,930
One is enough

12
00:01:13,490 --> 00:01:15,610
Didn't someone once say

13
00:01:16,810 --> 00:01:20,610
You need to bandage both fingers
so they won't feel lonely

14
00:01:33,250 --> 00:01:36,650
We're graduating soon

15
00:01:38,530 --> 00:01:41,410
Why don't we just get married?

16
00:01:44,289 --> 00:01:49,090
After I submit my thesis,
I'll take you straight to the district office

17
00:01:49,330 --> 00:01:50,729
To register our marriage

18
00:01:54,770 --> 00:01:57,690
The closest office to my home

19
00:01:57,690 --> 00:01:58,610
What?

20
00:01:59,539 --> 00:02:01,200
Who said I want to get married?

21
00:02:02,290 --> 00:02:03,160
Ow

22
00:02:05,750 --> 00:02:10,330
If you won't marry me,
I'll just kidnap you

23
00:02:16,370 --> 00:02:22,050
That works too, sounds exciting.
Just remember to put a black plastic bag over my head

24
00:02:36,010 --> 00:02:40,810
Why do you always leave
two leaves on your flowers?

25
00:02:40,810 --> 00:02:42,410
Take a guess

26
00:02:46,130 --> 00:02:53,050
Because you want them to be a pair,
just like the two of us, right?

27
00:02:55,370 --> 00:02:56,540
Well...

28
00:02:59,050 --> 00:03:00,820
It's just in case

29
00:03:06,610 --> 00:03:08,090
Because if someday

30
00:03:11,640 --> 00:03:16,770
One leaf withers first,
the other can still keep the flower company

31
00:03:17,810 --> 00:03:19,810
That way, the flower won't be lonely

32
00:03:20,530 --> 00:03:21,290
Right?
